reat color palette, and a love the slime expressions. The music really make you feel inside the dungedon and the sounds emphasize the visual.\u201d<br>SaulRib_<br>","screenshots":[{"id":0,"path_full":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455230/ss_5e71ab1895371fbd4ccf45afb23261624caf7bc8.1920x1080.jpg?t=1721597032","path_thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455230/ss_5e71ab1895371fbd4ccf45afb23261624caf7bc8.600x338.jpg?t=1721597032"},{"id":1,"path_full":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455230/ss_56c527c910011b6b656f73da6019f5212561b422.1920x1080.jpg?t=1721597032","path_thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455230/ss_56c527c910011b6b656f73da6019f5212561b422.600x338.jpg?t=1721597032"},{"id":2,"path_full":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455230/ss_7787b892b439f24d148ff3c2f8f2e20c35d81166.1920x1080.jpg?t=1721597032","path_thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455230/ss_7787b892b439f24d148ff3c2f8f2e20c35d81166.600x338.jpg?t=1721597032"},{"id":3,"path_full":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455230/ss_390d82677f4c9f8779a1e7dba9ce0ce3091af697.1920x1080.jpg?t=1721597032","path_thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455230/ss_390d82677f4c9f8779a1e7dba9ce0ce3091af697.600x338.jpg?t=1721597032"},{"id":4,"path_full":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455230/ss_493a2be6c6fb3b91044c23f052d287914135c8aa.1920x1080.jpg?t=1721597032","path_thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455230/ss_493a2be6c6fb3b91044c23f052d287914135c8aa.600x338.jpg?t=1721597032"},{"id":5,"path_full":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1455230/ss_3996712c9d919f6813e8d7ddb41f5d54c9b615d8.1920x1080.jpg?t=1721